Description:

    Generates files required for a new hydro message job for processing hydro
    messages placed in aqueduct by the aqueduct bridge.

Example:

    bin/rails generate hydro_message_job HydroOctochatLoginJob --topic "octochat.v0.Login" --service octochat

    This will create:

        app/jobs/hydro_octochat_login_job.rb
        test/jobs/hydro_octochat_login_job_test.rb

    Using the default queue name of `hydro_octochat_login` and the inferred
    message schema "octochat.v0.Login".

    The background job queue configuration for the service will be created (or updated)

      config/background_job_queues/octochat.yml

    It will also update configurations for the development and enterprise (if the --enterprise option is true)
    message bridge configurations:

      config/aqueduct_hydro_message_bridge/dotcom.yml
      config/aqueduct_hydro_message_bridge/enterprise.yml (if --enterprise option is true)
